title: 'The Challenge: Spies, Lies, and Allies’ Episode 6 With Fessy | Death, Taxes, and Bananas
description:
Former college football player and ‘The Challenge’ finalist Fessy joins Bananas this week to discuss Episode 6 of ‘Spies, Lies, and Allies.’ Fessy tells the story of when he was arrested as a college athlete (05:00), Bananas asks about Fessy’s disappointing end in ‘The Challenge’ final last season (36:00), and of course they discuss the altercation between Fessy and Josh in this week’s episode of ‘Spies, Lies, and Allies,’ along with Fessy’s budding romance with Amanda (55:00).
Host: Johnny Bananas
Guest: Fessy
Associate Producer: Sasha Ashall
Production Assistant: Jonathan Kermah
Additional Production: Juliet Litman
